tal town of Mpeketoni in eastern Kenya. June 16, 2014 In "News" Kenyan troops are "in control" of Nairobi's Westgate shopping mall, the Kenyan interior ministry announced overnight Monday, with all the hostages trapped by Islamist gunmen believed to have been freed. September 23, 2013 In "News" Kenyans and foreign nationals were among the 14 people killed in a bombing- and-gun attack on a high-end hotel complex in Nairobi overnight into Wednesday. January 16, 2019 In "News"